          "title": "Maltodextrin",
          "content": "<div class=\"prose max-w-none prose-green\"><h4>Vidhi 1: Iodine Abhikarmak ka Upyog Karna</h4><ol><li>Ek test tube mein 5 ml doodh ka sample lein.</li><li>2 ml iodine solution (0.05 N) dalein aur milayein.</li><li>Ek <strong>chocolate jaisa laal-bhura rang</strong> dextrin/maltodextrin ki maujoodgi ko darshata hai.</li></ol><h4 class=\"mt-4\">Vidhi 2: Citric Acid aur Iodine Abhikarmakon ka Upyog Karna</h4><ol><li>20 ml doodh ko ubaalein, 70°C par thanda karein, aur 0.5 ml 10% citric acid daalkar jamayein.</li><li>Jame hue doodh ko filter karein.</li><li>2 ml filtrate mein, iodine solution ki 3 boondein dalein.</li><li>Ek <strong>narangi-bhura rang</strong> maltodextrin ki maujoodgi ko darshata hai.</li></ol></div>"
